## LANDING PAGE CTAs

`RealLivesLanding.jsx` has two CTAs. Implement them exactly as follows:

### CTA 1 вЂ” "Buy License"
```jsx
<Link to="/reallives/licenses">Buy License</Link>
```
This navigates to `LicenseHub.jsx`.

### CTA 2 вЂ” "Login"
```jsx
<Link to="/reallives/login">Login</Link>
```
This navigates to `Login.jsx`.

Both CTAs are styled as buttons using CSS Modules. They are NOT `<a href>` tags.

